author: Capucilli,AlyssaSatin
title: Biscuit's My First I Can Read Book Collection
summary: Read along with Biscuit!     Let Biscuit introduce your child to the joys of independent reading. The little puppy's gentle nature and playful ways have made I Can Read#174; Biscuit books favorites with over a million emergent readers. With three great titles in one handy package, this collection is perfect for the newest reader in your family!
